<plot>In Turkey, wearing Islamic headscarf is banned from schools, universities and public offices in an effort to keep the country secular. The film follows the stories of four Turkish women who are devout Muslims and wear headscarves. A case study on secularism, democracy and modernism in a Muslim country.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?651867</url></doc>
